{"tid":1366344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港係一個中共未遇過既敵人","createTime":"2019-07-26T02:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T05:12:06.000Z","uid":35924,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3f902ecbb80eca4c60bc7760a0e0751e5fc385d3","tid":1366344,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:33:18.000Z","msg":"中共建國咁多年，維穩咁多年，8964同新疆果d，一直都係係中國入面封閉既環境到進行。相反係香港，資訊流通又有國際關注，唯一比唔上既就係人民既勇武。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地每行一步都係對中共既一個挑戰，話未有地方同勢力可以成功反共，不如話我地係唯一有望成功既一個地方！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n727 見，毋忘上環元朗義士"},{"pid":"27401a7584d8afd25b80a60d333f13f3f8f1d5b1","tid":1366344,"uid":127751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:35:29.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n清朝係香港開始推翻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990151a8f80cc1cca9dec44556634d17bd9e5aab","tid":1366344,"uid":8075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:35:54.000Z","msg":"大家一齊撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5469e65d804f8e91bc89e626572392728d6a0a19","tid":1366344,"uid":56323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:36:18.000Z","msg":"支那剩係識用軍隊清埸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c966f3ed9a8cde1be147c539d6222ad65688dbf0","tid":1366344,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:42:57.000Z","msg":"光復香港，我冇野講"},{"pid":"3490e7a33eb64f40f507f5982063afdda7ac81ea","tid":1366344,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:07:22.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"c396f60abf772d24fd2b1f7b57aaf55e2406d97d","tid":1366344,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:09:15.000Z","msg":"ppp"},{"pid":"81ee41535651de2709f3041cce63c6399068a5d5","tid":1366344,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:12:06.000Z","msg":"記得新疆好似有憎人暴動過<br